high_descs: Turn around and face the counter next to the stove.
Grab the knife from the counter.
Turn around and walk then turn left and face the table.
Slice the lettuce that is on the table.
Turn around and face the fridge
Place the knife in the fridge.
Head back to the table.
Grab a lettuce slice from the table.
Turn left back to the fridge.
Chill the lettuce slice in the fridge for 3 seconds.
Turn around and walk then walk right to face the table.
Place the lettuce slice on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled lettuce slice on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter that is left of the stove.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter.
Turn around, go across the room, hang a left and go to the end of the white table where the tomato is.
Cut the lettuce on the table into slices.
Turn to the left, go forward to the fridge that is on the left.
Put the knife inside the fridge.
Turn to the left, go to the table where the lettuce is.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the table.
Turn to the left, go forward to the fridge that is on the left.
Put the lettuce inside the fridge and close the door, take the lettuce out of the fridge once it is cold.
Turn around, go forward, turn to the right at the table where the black stool is.
Put the lettuce on the table to the left of the head of lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Put cold lettuce on a table.

high_descs: Turn around, go to the counter
Pick up the knife on the counter
Turn around, go forward, turn left, go forward, turn left at the table
Slice the lettuce on the table
Turn left, go to the fridge
Put the knife in the fridge
Turn left, go to the table
Pick up a lettuce slice from the table
Turn left, go to the fridge
Put the lettuce slice in the fridge, wait, pick up the lettuce slice from the fridge
Turn around, go forward, turn right at the table
Put the lettuce slice on the table
anns.task_desc: Slice a lettuce, cool a slice
